{"tid":970768,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"街頭測試英國人紳士程度　男女平等仲講咩風度","createTime":"2019-01-06T06:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T17:06:42.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f59bee53d9dfb0d64bab5042c5dc26f03d7dc885","tid":970768,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"英國的男士出名有紳士風度，推門、讓女士先行、請客等禮貌等等被視為基本禮儀，不過有些香港男士就不大同意。網上討論區曾有人拋題：「覺不覺得外國人幫人推門是虛偽？」不少留言一面倒認為無必要為女士推門。我們分別在倫敦和香港兩地做街頭實驗及街訪，實測廿一世紀的男士會否傳承「紳士風度」的傳統價值。即刻去片參考現今英國和香港男女的看法！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190104/large/1546593290_4e21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190104%2Flarge%2F1546593290_4e21.jpg&h=3434f4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者在繁忙時間於倫敦和香港的商業區搬行李上落樓梯，測試路人會否主動提出幫忙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190104/large/1546593290_95e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190104%2Flarge%2F1546593290_95e1.png&h=2d1a1b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即使在以紳士文化聞名的英國，亦只是間中遇到人主動出手幫忙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190104/large/1546593290_774d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190104%2Flarge%2F1546593290_774d.png&h=0376489e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國是西方社會「紳士風度」的發源地，推門、讓女士先行、請客等禮貌等等被視為基本禮儀。<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳海利<br />\n攝影：吳詠音<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190106/59105150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59105150&d=mSCPsj%2BCpXNT31el%2F4C9KleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=2d046fbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59105150&h=304012c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190106/59105150</a>"},{"pid":"ba9a4c8442e055b953b604da43fd36ebb3178268","tid":970768,"uid":21629,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"係美國 見到不論男女都會幫人推門<br />\n係香港 啲人淨係見到門就閂就拿拿聲衝入去唔想推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae676cac43f833b5337162fafc9af4515607c62","tid":970768,"uid":30710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"不愧係大英帝國嘅子民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc71c755fd66945fcf7fbf7ea70210804fccf90","tid":970768,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9a4c8442e055b953b604da43fd36ebb3178268","tid":970768,"uid":21629,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"係美國 見到不論男女都會幫人推門<br />\n係香港 啲人淨係見到門就閂就拿拿聲衝入去唔想推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"連啲男人都係zip入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d4edc2a8c40cea3b9004d99c124c0f8d77b0cb","tid":970768,"uid":154783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba9a4c8442e055b953b604da43fd36ebb3178268","tid":970768,"uid":21629,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"係美國 見到不論男女都會幫人推門<br />\n係香港 啲人淨係見到門就閂就拿拿聲衝入去唔想推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"有無諗過唔係人地唔想推埋<br />\n而係後面啲人閪晒臉老奉等你開埋門咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm